<h2 id="get-ready-with-the-latest-beta-releases">Get ready with the latest beta releases
</h2><p>December 16, 2024</p>
<p>The beta versions of iOS 18.3, iPadOS 18.3, macOS 15.3, tvOS 18.3, visionOS 2.3, and watchOS 11.3 are now available. Get your apps ready by confirming they work as expected on these releases. And to take advantage of the advancements in the latest SDKs, make sure to build and test with Xcode 16.2.</p>
